1
00:00:01,025 --> 00:00:04,335
You think you know a story,
but you only know how it ends.

2
00:00:05,305 --> 00:00:09,537
To get to the heart of the story,
you have to go back to the beginning.

3
00:01:27,385 --> 00:01:29,182
My lords.

4
00:01:30,225 --> 00:01:32,819
In the absence
of the queen herself...

5
00:01:33,025 --> 00:01:35,539
...whom this tribunal
has pronounced contumacious...

6
00:01:35,745 --> 00:01:38,782
...since she does not appear
when summoned.

7
00:01:38,985 --> 00:01:40,976
We are trying to determine
whether or not...

8
00:01:41,185 --> 00:01:43,062
...her first marriage
to Prince Arthur...

9
00:01:43,265 --> 00:01:48,339
...was in fact
consummated in carnal copula.

10
00:01:48,545 --> 00:01:51,981
We call a witness.
Sir Anthony Willoughby.

11
00:02:02,225 --> 00:02:06,503
I understand you were in the escort
taking Prince Arthur to the nuptial bed?

12
00:02:06,745 --> 00:02:10,340
I was, sir. My father was at the time
steward of the king's household.

13
00:02:10,585 --> 00:02:17,024
So, I was present when the prince was
inserted into Lady Catherine's bed...

14
00:02:17,225 --> 00:02:19,864
...and also
when he woke in the morning.

15
00:02:20,105 --> 00:02:24,178
And did the prince say anything to you
when you saw him in the morning?

16
00:02:24,385 --> 00:02:27,377
Yes, sir.
He said, "Willoughby, I'm thirsty.

17
00:02:27,585 --> 00:02:32,784
Bring me a cup of ale.
Last night, I was in the midst of Spain."

18
00:02:34,905 --> 00:02:39,217
Silence. Silence in the court.

19
00:02:43,265 --> 00:02:45,654
- Anything else?
- Yes, sir.

20
00:02:45,905 --> 00:02:52,014
Later that day he said to us, " Masters,
it's a good pastime to have a wife."

21
00:02:53,625 --> 00:02:56,185
Silence in the court.

22
00:02:57,345 --> 00:03:01,896
I believe we may have the bloodstained
sheets to corroborate my lord's story.

23
00:03:02,105 --> 00:03:06,815
That would be most useful,
Your Eminence. Most useful.

24
00:03:41,945 --> 00:03:44,857
- Your Majesty.
- Gentlemen.

25
00:03:45,105 --> 00:03:48,097
The king asks
why you are not in court.

26
00:03:48,345 --> 00:03:50,415
I have given answer to that already.

27
00:03:52,185 --> 00:03:54,301
- Could we go somewhere private?
- Why?

28
00:03:54,505 --> 00:03:55,824
I have nothing to hide.

29
00:03:56,025 --> 00:03:59,495
Let my ladies and the whole world
hear what you have to say.

30
00:04:00,465 --> 00:04:05,141
The king commands that you surrender
this whole matter into his hands.

31
00:04:05,345 --> 00:04:08,143
Otherwise, the court
will condemn you.

32
00:04:08,345 --> 00:04:10,381
I am surprised to receive
such a request...

33
00:04:10,585 --> 00:04:13,702
...from such wise
and noble men as you.

34
00:04:13,905 --> 00:04:18,456
I am but a poor woman,
lacking both in wit and understanding.

35
00:04:18,665 --> 00:04:21,816
How am I supposed to respond to
a request made to me out of the blue?

36
00:04:22,025 --> 00:04:24,937
You know perfectly what the king
desires and what he shall have.

37
00:04:25,145 --> 00:04:28,103
All I know, Eminence, is that you...

38
00:04:28,305 --> 00:04:30,500
...for your own purposes,
have kindled this fire.

39
00:04:30,705 --> 00:04:33,458
All this time, all these years...

40
00:04:33,705 --> 00:04:37,584
...I have wondered at your high pride
and your vain glory.

41
00:04:37,825 --> 00:04:40,578
I have abhorred your voluptuous life
and had no regard...

42
00:04:40,785 --> 00:04:43,504
...for your presumptuous power
and your tyranny.

43
00:04:43,705 --> 00:04:46,902
I know also of your malice
against my nephew, the emperor.

44
00:04:47,105 --> 00:04:50,575
You hate him like a scorpion.
And why?

45
00:04:51,385 --> 00:04:55,094
Because he would not satisfy your
ambition and make you pope by force.

46
00:04:55,305 --> 00:04:56,943
You should never presume to know...

47
00:04:57,145 --> 00:04:59,375
My only satisfaction
is that in frustrating you...

48
00:04:59,585 --> 00:05:01,894
...I hasten your fall
from the king's good graces.

49
00:05:02,105 --> 00:05:06,223
An outcome I desire
above all others.

50
00:05:13,305 --> 00:05:17,776
Hold, Your Eminence.
You will not get your divorce this way.

51
00:05:18,705 --> 00:05:21,060
It is the only way.

52
00:05:29,745 --> 00:05:33,374
Friend, give me a drink. I'm thirsty.

53
00:05:34,185 --> 00:05:38,098
And if you'd all been to Spain as many
times as I went there last night...

54
00:05:38,345 --> 00:05:40,415
...you'd all be fucking thirsty too.

55
00:05:43,145 --> 00:05:45,613
In and out, in and out, in and out.

56
00:05:46,505 --> 00:05:49,019
And I'll tell you this, lads.

57
00:05:51,145 --> 00:05:54,899
First time I lay with a lady
I was but a chit of a lad.

58
00:05:55,105 --> 00:05:59,542
